            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Dedicated by Publius Veidius Pollio, an attested friend of Augustus (Cass. Dio 54.23; Sen. Ira 3.40; Sen. Clem. 1.18.2; Plin. HN. 9.77; Tert. Pall. 5)</p> 
